==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ravenous
<hw>Rav"en*ous</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧v"'n*⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[From 2d <er>Raven</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Devouring with
rapacious eagerness; furiously voracious; hungry even to rage; <as>as, a
<ex>ravenous</ex> wolf or vulture</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Eager for prey or gratification; <as>as, a
<ex>ravenous</ex> appetite or desire</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Rav"en*ous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Rav"en*ous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Raven's-duck</ent>⟦br⟧
